data.description: A FANTASTIC Cozy Ranch Home with 4 bdrms and 2 full bath sitting on almost a 1/4 acre lot. Prepare meals in the renovated kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances, Granite Counter Top with a Breakfast Bar, and ample space of cabinetry. A Primary Bedroom with its own Private bath and 3 more rooms to choose from. Celebrate with family and friends in your huge fenced in back yard. Commute w/ convenience of close access to I-64, health care, childcare, restaurants, shopping centers, Portsmouth Shipyard, Portsmouth Medical Center, and new Rivers Casino. Renovations has already been done from roofing to window to bathroom, and LVP flooring. Come see for yourself this MOVE IN Ready home today.  SELLER OFFERING $2,000 FLOORING ALLOWANCE.
